ity klaus mittenzwei university of oslo anna stenport university of gothenburg and university of illinois at urbana champaign damon tojjar lund university past anna lindh fellowship recipients 2010 2011 vibeke kieding banik university of oslo thomas jonter stockholm university susanna rabow edling uppsala university daniel schatz humboldt university berlin 2009 2010 abebe gellaw independent scholar anu mai koll sodertorn university jonas linde university of gothenburg dalia marcinkeviciene vilnius university laust schouenborg london school of economics patricia rinwigati waagstein uppsala university 2008 2009 li bennich bjorkman uppsala university stefan hedlund uppsala university nils muiznieks university of latvia 2007 2008 patricia rinwigati uppsala university erik noreen uppsala university the europe center accepts applications for the anna lindh fellowship on an ongoing basis please visit the fellowship page for more details search search within everything courses events fellowships news op eds people publications research other pages more information anna lindh fellowship fsi stanford the europe center fellowship for professionals international scholars support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 724 9656 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
